.img [downloadable](http://download.webconverger.com/) files are USB-hdd images for hardware able to boot from a USB stick/key.

[How to copy .img to USB stick](http://wiki.debian.org/DebianLive/Howto/USB). 

* Works only with newer computers
* Just as fast as a hard drive in many cases

